"{\"uid\": \"salon.com-2024-08-02-olympics-boxing-controversy-gender\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Another controversy has engulfed the 2024 ParisOlympicsbut this time it involves gender and boxing.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 99, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"False allegations have been swirling around conservative media outlets and online spaces that Algerian boxer Imane Khelif is a transgender woman in the women's competition.\", \"from\": 101, \"to\": 273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 195, \"end\": 203, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9990595165283147, \"rank\": 0.0009406495016169256, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Right-wing conservative figures likeDonald Trump,Elon Musk,J.K.\", \"from\": 274, \"to\": 337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 323, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elon Musk\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elon_Musk\"}, {\"begin\": 333, \"end\": 337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.3018841075831193e-28, \"text\": \"J.K.\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/J._K._Rowling\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rowlingand many others have openly perpetuated this conspiracy theory online.\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 415, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The controversy began when the fight between\\u00c2\\u00a0Italian boxer Angela Carini and Khelif swiftly ended after a mere 46 seconds on Thursday.\", \"from\": 417, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 463, \"end\": 470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9993715006570344, \"rank\": 0.0005979649222610369, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 490, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini broke out in tears and left the ring, withdrawing from the match.\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 553, \"end\": 559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999998585736, \"rank\": 1.414891265502901e-10, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After the match, she told reporters, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was told a lot of times that I was a warrior but I preferred to stop for my health.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never felt a punch like this,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The Hollywood Reporterreported.\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 823, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini has sincepublically apologizedto Khelif in an interview with an Italian newspaper,\\u00c2\\u00a0Gazzetta dello Sport.\", \"from\": 825, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 825, \"end\": 831, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999998585736, \"rank\": 1.414891265502901e-10, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 896, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.9993715006570344, \"rank\": 0.0005979649222610369, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said, \\\"I am sorry for my opponent, too.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 981, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the [The International Olympic Committee] said she can fight, I respect that decision,\\\" The BBCreported.\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1089, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1025, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related  About dropping out of the match, she said, \\\"It wasn't something I intended to do.\", \"from\": 1091, \"to\": 1181, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Actually, I want to apologize to her and everyone else.\", \"from\": 1182, \"to\": 1237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was angry because my Olympics had gone up in smoke.\", \"from\": 1238, \"to\": 1291, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t have anything against Khelif.\", \"from\": 1292, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Actually, if I were to meet her again I would embrace her.\\\"\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1391, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Carini's withdrawal has ignited a gender-centered culture war.\", \"from\": 1393, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1402, \"end\": 1408, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999999998585736, \"rank\": 1.414891265502901e-10, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her opponent, Khelif, is one of two boxers allowed to compete in Paris after being disqualified from the women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s world championships in 2023 for failing testosterone and gender eligibility tests.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1530, \"end\": 1535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999431566, \"rank\": 5.680420729337225e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC called the decision to bar Khelif and another boxer from the championship as a \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009csudden and arbitrary decision,\\\" USA Todayreported.\\u00c2  Khelif was raised as and identifies as a woman and is not transgender nor intersex.\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1889, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1667, \"end\": 1670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017990584248657e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to theIOC, Khelif has a difference in\\u00c2\\u00a0sexual development (DSD), which is not the same as being transgender.\", \"from\": 1890, \"to\": 2008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1959, \"end\": 1962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.5669211124186002, \"rank\": 0.7639138463793778, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This can mean that some people who develop as a woman can also have XY chromosomes.\", \"from\": 2009, \"to\": 2092, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite women with DSD currently being allowed to compete in women's sports at the Olympics, that has not stopped conservative media from misgendering Khelif.\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2251, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2112, \"end\": 2115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"score\": 0.5669211124186002, \"rank\": 0.7639138463793778, \"text\": \"DSD\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Direct_Stream_Digital\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Musk has posted\\u00c2multiple times on X\\u00c2\\u00a0about the match between the women.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He argued, \\\"Men don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t belong in women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sports.\\\"\", \"from\": 2325, \"to\": 2377, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a series of tweets, Rowling also misgendered Khelif.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2434, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The author posted a picture of the two women, stating, \\\"Could any picture sum up our new men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s rights movement better?\", \"from\": 2435, \"to\": 2555, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The smirk of a male who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s knows he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s protected by a misogynist sporting establishment enjoying the distress of a woman he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just punched in the head, and whose life\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s ambition he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just shattered.\\\"\", \"from\": 2556, \"to\": 2763, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Could any picture sum up our new men\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s rights movement better?\", \"from\": 2765, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The smirk of a male who\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s knows he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s protected by a misogynist sporting establishment enjoying the distress of a woman he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just punched in the head, and whose life\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s ambition he\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s just shattered.#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/Q5SbKiksXQ  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 J.K. Rowling (@jk_rowling)August 1, 2024    In another post, Rowling said, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cA young female boxer has just had everything she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s worked and trained for snatched away because [the IOC] allowed a male to get in the ring with her.\\\"\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 3308, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017990584248657e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A young female boxer has just had everything she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s worked and trained for snatched away because you allowed a male to get in the ring with her.\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3455, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re a disgrace, your \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098safeguarding\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 is a joke and#Paris24will be forever tarnished by the brutal injustice done to Carini.https://t.co/JMKzVljpyr  \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 J.K. Rowling (@jk_rowling)August 1, 2024    Trump has also posted\\u00c2on Truth Social, \\u00c2\\u00a0\\\"I will keep men out of women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sports!\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The Republican presidential nominee once said on \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d that \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cwhat gets the biggest applause\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d at his rallies is saying, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe will not allow men to play in women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s sports,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Rolling Stonereported.\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3986, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3750, \"end\": 3760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"score\": 0.9975647917939335, \"rank\": 0.002441152175971568, \"text\": \"Republican\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Second_Spanish_Republic\"}, {\"begin\": 3818, \"end\": 3829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Jesse_Kelly_Show\", \"score\": 0.9923626680862244, \"rank\": 0.007696109657728145, \"text\": \"Buck Sexton\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q1555508\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Jesse_Kelly_Show\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Jesse_Kelly_Show\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the misgendering of Khelif, the IOC issued a statement defending\\u00c2\\u00a0her and the other disqualified boxer, Taiwan's Lin Yu-ting.\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe IOC is saddened by the abuse that the two athletes are currently receiving.\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 4205, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4028, \"end\": 4031, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017990584248657e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4100, \"end\": 4106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"score\": 0.9999904939856411, \"rank\": 9.201902354350405e-06, \"text\": \"Taiwan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taiwan\"}, {\"begin\": 4130, \"end\": 4133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017990584248657e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every person has the right to practice sport without discrimination,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d it read.\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4286, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We obviously condemn the harassment of which [Khelif] is a victim.\", \"from\": 4287, \"to\": 4354, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hate, denigration and insults are the opposite of the values we defend.\\\"\", \"from\": 4355, \"to\": 4427, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The IOC's spokesperson Mark Adams also\\u00c2urgedpeople on Friday to be more mindful about discussing Khelif and Lin.\\u00c2\\u00a0\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWhat I would urge is that we try to take the culture war out of this and actually address the issues and think about the individuals and the people concerned.\", \"from\": 4429, \"to\": 4704, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4433, \"end\": 4436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5017990584248657e-30, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4452, \"end\": 4462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"score\": 0.5137413298826524, \"rank\": 0.45833333333321225, \"text\": \"Mark Adams\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mark_Adams_(basketball,_born_May_1956)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Real damage is being done by misinformation.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Marks reiterated, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe Algerian boxer was born a female, was registered a female, lived her life as a female, boxed as a female, has a female passport.\", \"from\": 4705, \"to\": 4907, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4779, \"end\": 4787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9990595165283147, \"rank\": 0.0009406495016169256, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is not a transgender case.\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4939, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There has been some confusion that somehow it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a man fighting a woman.\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 5013, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This is just not the case, scientifically on that, there is consensus.\", \"from\": 5014, \"to\": 5084, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Scientifically, this is not a man fighting a woman.\", \"from\": 5085, \"to\": 5136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And I think we need to kind of get that out.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Also, Adams clarified that gender eligibility is an unsatisfactory system, dubbing it as a \\\"minefield.\\\"\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5289, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued, \\\"There are many women with higher [testosterone] levels than men so the idea that a testosterone test is some kind of magic bullet is not true.\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"\\u00c2  Read more  about this topic  \\u00c2  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2026 Salon.com, LLC.\", \"from\": 5447, \"to\": 5516, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5501, \"end\": 5510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Salon.com\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Salon.com\"}, {\"begin\": 5512, \"end\": 5515, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Limited_liability_